:"HK PR 其實點解一定中國籍？ <br />\n外國PR =/= citizenship<br />\n定香港仆街啲當PR係citizen?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"永居=/=中籍<br />\n中籍係香港出世有華人血統既香港居民"},{"pid":"102e3cb8b4d970e115b426bc6f402ef341c71db7","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"90d976de174356aa2551534db456132fd93cbebd","tid":2394731,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d63c8ec8ee9112f8ff6e0d79cc699e035be5eb3","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aebc93bfe85bcb576c63384a207dd0a47a890f8","tid":2394731,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"即係身份證唔一定中國或香港籍？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n<br />\n因為現行《人事登記條例》同《入境條例》都無將居留權同國籍掛勾。即係話你係外籍既話，喺香港住滿七年如喬寶寶老婆咁都係拎得到永居身分證<br />\n<br />\n另外ROP1/2/3表格-即各身份證申請表格上第7項已經需要申請人申報國籍，即係話走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n哩個page都有研究開國籍，不妨睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1504977279705168/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1504977279705168%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=ae9eb6f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1504977279705168/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"咁即係佢應該揀加籍 放棄中國籍<br />\n做加拿大籍有香港居留權既人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁即係要取消埋特區護照"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n所以最好就係入紙取消中籍還廁板同歡樂卡，有d野貪左就好大代價，千祈唔好貪"},{"pid":"85a150169ca13240b0ea8e504b861b23aa66c2f8","tid":2394731,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"caa2dc2c3abb3dbd7454672702074287be994020","tid":2394731,"uid":170187,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"HK PR 其實點解一定中國籍？ <br />\n外國PR =/= citizenship<br />\n定香港仆街啲當PR係citizen?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"97年畀nmslese強姦inject咗"},{"pid":"efe0d2b4305b39594e88cd13d574ebe58ac92426","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca4609771831d3fa6006722662ce9592ca30e29","tid":2394731,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29bcde3bec206b1e99305eb9b96d9df2736b5f82","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"喺現行法例之下仲係可以雙重國籍，但係如果有中國籍既話喺中港澳都會係中國籍人士，唔可以獲得領事保護。<br />\n<br />\n不過今日加拿大政府已經證實港府開始搵人試水溫，所以樓主既加籍朋友應該要諗下留中國籍定加籍，反正最後都要犧牲是但一樣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"去到台灣呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"台灣係計華籍<br />\n注意華籍=/=中國籍，係類似外籍但唔係完全承認"},{"pid":"3fb5ac94f43977645b4f76597f81dca00c779dc5","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85a150169ca13240b0ea8e504b861b23aa66c2f8","tid":2394731,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"caa2dc2c3abb3dbd7454672702074287be994020","tid":2394731,"uid":170187,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"HK PR 其實點解一定中國籍？ <br />\n外國PR =/= citizenship<br />\n定香港仆街啲當PR係citizen?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"97年畀nmslese強姦inject咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\n正確係1996年實施既全國人民代表大會常務委員會關於《中華人民共和國國籍法》在香港特別行政區實施的幾個問題的解釋<br />\n<br />\n第一條已經咁寫<br />\n//凡具有中國血統的香港居民，本人出生在中國領土（含香港）者，以及其他符合《中華人民共和國國籍法》規定的具有中國國籍的條件者，都是中國公民。//"},{"pid":"86c622136df70df4cfacb5abc5da993bfe4676e1","tid":2394731,"uid":58235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"問16 : 假如我在換領身份證時在申請表上「申報的國籍」一欄填上外國國籍，新身份證上的「***」或「*」符號會否被取消？<br />\n<br />\n新身份證上的「***」或「*」符號不會因為在申請表上填寫外國國籍而被取消。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c87ee112394e06039e844e98b9ca548e2cd9c8a","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86c622136df70df4cfacb5abc5da993bfe4676e1","tid":2394731,"uid":58235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"問16 : 假如我在換領身份證時在申請表上「申報的國籍」一欄填上外國國籍，新身份證上的「***」或「*」符號會否被取消？<br />\n<br />\n新身份證上的「***」或「*」符號不會因為在申請表上填寫外國國籍而被取消。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"所以點解一直都話想要領事保護就一定要去入境處做埋退中籍，反正三粒星都喺度，怕咩"},{"pid":"822830b06fd54b92e8c604b7d8c9f54b76d9bf7c","tid":2394731,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe0d2b4305b39594e88cd13d574ebe58ac92426","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca4609771831d3fa6006722662ce9592ca30e29","tid":2394731,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29bcde3bec206b1e99305eb9b96d9df2736b5f82","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"喺現行法例之下仲係可以雙重國籍，但係如果有中國籍既話喺中港澳都會係中國籍人士，唔可以獲得領事保護。<br />\n<br />\n不過今日加拿大政府已經證實港府開始搵人試水溫，所以樓主既加籍朋友應該要諗下留中國籍定加籍，反正最後都要犧牲是但一樣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"去到台灣呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"台灣係計華籍<br />\n注意華籍=/=中國籍，係類似外籍但唔係完全承認"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"BNO = 華籍？"},{"pid":"93f97224622982afefe44109ddf5a0362cafae8d","tid":2394731,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822830b0